  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Steiner is deservedly popular with Inghams guests for its large leisure area and excellent reputation for service and cuisine.</p>
<h2>Warm welcome</h2>
<p>Run by the friendly Steiner family, you will be made to feel most welcome here. The hotel has a superb location two minutes' walk from the centre of <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/4449c10aa6834800bdfa1f1806a57e96" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4449c10aa6834800bdfa1f1806a57e96}" target="_blank" title="Obertauern">Obertauern</a> and slopes just across the road.</p>
<h2>Infinity pool </h2>
<p>The Hotel Steiner has recently invested in a new adults-only spa area. The wellness area is complete with a rooftop infinity pool, Finnish sauna, organic sauna, Roman tepidarium, steam bath, rock crystal grotto and relaxation area.</p>
<h2>Kids' paradise</h2>
<p>The Steiner family pride themselves on being a family-friendly hotel run by a family. While parents can spend some time relaxing in the spa area, kids can explore the play room and games room.</p>
<p>The youth lounge has a climbing wall, games consoles, air hockey, and table football. New for this season, the indoor forest playground has a wood workshop, indoor mud room, and painting studio.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Steiner the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
